Article.ArticleTitle: A Concise Asymmetric Total Synthesis of (+)-Epilupinine.

AbstractText: Asymmetric total synthesis of (+)-epilupinine was achieved in just three steps using only commercially available common reagents. The total synthesis involved alkylations of N-nosylamide, ozone oxidation, and sequential reactions of the removal of the nosyl group, intramolecular dehydrative condensation, intramolecular Mannich reaction catalyzed by l-proline, and a reduction.
